{"tid":227901,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打養緊穀牛？","createTime":"2017-05-03T13:38:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T13:59:32.000Z","uid":3363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51fc3117f46c5ba66569b21ae15d619e22e57d11","tid":227901,"uid":3363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKdvvc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKdvvc9.jpg&h=c33e44f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，最近執屋係櫃桶搵到一小袋唔知擺左幾耐既米。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發現有幾隻穀牛係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後見佢地咁可愛決定試下養下佢地，但想問小小野<br />\n<br />\n1.我洗唔洗補米入去，驚佢地會蛀曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.我洗唔洗比d空氣佢地，因為密實袋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3.有冇咩特別野要注意，始終叫第一次養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2496c9e6368e4da235003cea088198b4bd21f16e","tid":227901,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T13:43:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZKdvvc9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZKdvvc9.jpg&h=c33e44f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，最近執屋係櫃桶搵到一小袋唔知擺左幾耐既米。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 發現有幾隻穀牛係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後見佢地咁可愛決定試下養下佢地，但想問小小野<br />\n<br />\n1.我洗唔洗補米入去，驚佢地會蛀曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2.我洗唔洗比d空氣佢地，因為密實袋黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3.有冇咩特別野要注意，始終叫第一次養<img src=\"/assets/fac